. The goal is not the make serve fully runtime agnostic.\n\n## Solution\n\nThis PR adds Serve::with_executor() and WithGracefulShutdown::with_executor() builder methods that take an Executor, and an axum::serve::Executor trait for defining the Executor interface.\n\nThe default remains a new TokioExecutor (that spawns tokio spawns just like before), so we maintain backward compatibility.\n\nSmall design note: this defines a new axum::serve::Executor trait rather than reuse of hyper::rt::Executor<Fut> directly, because the latter is generic at the trait level and I couldn't find a way to bound E to cover all the internal future types hyper needs. So this new trait uses a generic method instead, and then a HyperExecutor<E> adapter bridges to hyper.","verified_at":"2026-04-20T12:49:31Z"}},"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/tokio-rs/axum/commits/de9f13d809e86f8bf24292aac0af16d97ef91195","html_url":"https://github.com/tokio-rs/axum/commit/de9f13d809e86f8bf24292aac0af16d97ef91195","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/tokio-rs/axum/commits/de9f13d809e86f8bf24292aac0af16d97ef91195/comments","author":{"login":"yulnr","id":22042418,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIyMDQyNDE4","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/22042418?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/yulnr","html_url":"https://github.com/yulnr","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yulnr/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yulnr/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yulnr/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yulnr/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yulnr/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yulnr/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yulnr/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yulnr/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yulnr/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","sit